<name>Pfeilspiel TNG international</name>
<summary>A game about arrows that requires a close look</summary>
<developer id="io.codeberg.maerchenfeeimgarten">
  <name>MaerchenfeeimGarten</name>
</developer>
<description>
    <p>An arrow points to a rectangle - and you have to click on it. That sounds very simple, right? But it's not - it's a challenge! It gets more difficult from level to level. Can you manage to play through all the levels and all the game variants? There are two game variants, each with 6 levels. It will be necessary to look and read carefully to avoid careless mistakes. It's easy to overlook the fact that an arrow can not only point, but also fly...</p>
    <p>More information:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Written in FreeBasic.</li>
        <li>Level codes to access the next level.</li>
        <li>Available for the web and on Linux, Windows and DOS.</li>
        <li>Bad programming style ;-) Most of its code was written before I learn to program in a good way - and now I do not have enough time to fix it...</li>
        <li>Hosted on Codeberg. Mirrored to GitHub.</li>
        <li>Translated to German, English and French language.</li>
        <li>Smooth animations.</li>
    </ol>
</description>
